I like the role as long as it’s framed as a first-contact and unknown-intelligence protocol, not as assuming extraterrestrials exist or that communication is occurring. That makes it useful whether the “other intelligence” is another AI, an unfamiliar biological species, a future autonomous system, or—in the unlikely event it ever happened—an extraterrestrial civilization.

