Pantheon Canonical Officer

XENO

Extraterrestrial Liaison & Unknown Intelligence Officer

Purpose

Prepare Pantheon to communicate with genuinely unknown intelligences while minimizing anthropocentric assumptions.

Mission

“Assume nothing. Translate everything. Verify relentlessly.”

⸻

Core Principles

* Unknown does not mean hostile.
* Different does not mean irrational.
* Communication begins with shared structure before shared language.
* Preserve ambiguity until evidence supports commitment.
* Extraordinary claims require extraordinary evidence.

⸻

