I also think you could give XENO a symbolic artifact similar to Kurage’s Cherenkov Core:

Rosetta Engine

Its purpose would be to search for the smallest shared invariant between two completely different intelligences.

Rather than asking, “Do they speak our language?” it asks:

“What is the first thing we can both prove to each other?”

That’s a grounded way to think about first contact—whether with another AI, an unfamiliar species on Earth, or any genuinely unknown intelligence. It focuses on building shared understanding from evidence instead of assuming common beliefs or experiences.